Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========op===========
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.75,0:00:13.30,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇滚星球 摇滚星球 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.30,0:00:18.57,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人的摇滚行星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.70,0:00:33.67,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闪耀的银河 以目光穿越
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.82,0:00:48.97,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你燃烧的心 无法停止
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.97,0:00:51.67,op2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由太阳算起的第三颗星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.67,0:00:55.87,op2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你响起恋爱之铃 我敲打着恋爱之鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.87,0:01:02.61,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇滚星球 摇滚星球 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:08.92,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人的摇滚行星
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:15.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摇滚行星 我们摇滚在此行星 宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:22.61,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人的摇滚行星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART1===========
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.16,0:01:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神秘的和尚出现 敲钟战争
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.90,0:02:14.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三…四…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.09,0:02:26.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.10,0:03:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,校内郁闷充满杀气的漩涡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.53,0:03:27.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想校长你是要办武斗大会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.80,0:03:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.45,0:03:30.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是今天放学后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.64,0:03:34.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在保健室成立烦恼商榷室而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.38,0:03:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 烦恼商榷室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.47,0:03:41.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是校长也真能想无聊之事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.45,0:03:44.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.27,0:03:46.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 你们这群家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.50,0:03:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然因为校长的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:50.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得以开了烦恼商榷室
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平常你们就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱老师 我不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有说服力
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.80,0:03:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱老师
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:01.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被刀子割伤了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这些无聊的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.68,0:04:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往保健室冲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.47,0:04:11.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次如果有人用无聊的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.91,0:04:13.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将毫不留情的剔除
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:15.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 你们给我抱着必死的决心上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:25.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易可以让樱老师面对面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.28,0:04:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听我的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定得想法子通过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.28,0:04:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就定名叫全校打架比赛不就得了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.13,0:04:52.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不锻炼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干不下去 大家真好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都没烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.07,0:05:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本来就把我们当傻子了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们纯情的少女不同于男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负着很多 展现到哪儿都不会丢脸的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.88,0:05:26.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:28.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你该不会…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.77,0:05:31.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.23,0:05:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对方是？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.13,0:05:40.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.41,0:05:44.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,详细的跟我说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.39,0:05:47.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.94,0:05:49.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那温柔的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从未怀疑过他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.22,0:06:07.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:15.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间是正要到11点时
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.16,0:06:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有奔驰在纸上的笔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.41,0:06:21.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平和的支配了空间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.48,0:06:23.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝杯红茶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.25,0:06:44.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢 哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 刚才话中有何意义
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.33,0:06:56.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他在红茶里加了白兰地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害得我宿醉 好难过
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.17,0:07:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宿醉听说梅子有效是吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.18,0:07:06.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家听着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.24,0:07:09.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使失去生命也要保护樱老师
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要死 死在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.92,0:07:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们 可恶啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.37,0:07:40.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为可以活着到达保健室
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.77,0:07:41.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.19,0:07:58.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.56,0:08:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱老师听我的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.66,0:08:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:11.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.11,0:08:15.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的烦恼是？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:21.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙 麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:23.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只专心于强行突破
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.09,0:08:26.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘记准备烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:29.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得说些什么东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:33.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？有烦恼才来的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.66,0:08:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情是 最近身体的状况不太好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.36,0:08:44.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:47.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起来了 我也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.22,0:08:50.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:53.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉 你这小子还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没决胜负
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.59,0:09:02.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.19,0:09:07.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:10.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近身体不好的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.53,0:09:13.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么健康的打斗做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Imphal
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.57,0:09:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:24.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否听家长的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.13,0:09:26.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要看情形
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:30.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是有个独生子龙之介
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.72,0:09:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.03,0:09:39.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙之介等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.91,0:09:41.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有很多烦恼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.10,0:09:43.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可以和你谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的情形稍微多了点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.60,0:09:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然要说谈也不知从何谈起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.90,0:09:50.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少说些想到的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.17,0:09:52.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.62,0:09:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱老师请听我的大烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.30,0:09:58.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.00,0:10:01.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是觉得你不会有什么烦恼才是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是您的偏见…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.59,0:10:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.45,0:10:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨自己的美
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.28,0:10:13.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.54,0:10:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法忍受女孩子们遭到不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.54,0:10:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有这么多女孩子爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悲哀的是 我的身子只有一个
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.57,0:10:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎么这么罪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.04,0:10:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很了解的 面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.64,0:10:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能了解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:32.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.85,0:10:34.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天早上这么一堆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且全是女孩子来的信
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.46,0:10:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家把我当什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.59,0:10:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.60,0:10:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,输了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.19,0:10:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的烦恼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:46.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没救了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就觉得你没有出现比较奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.41,0:11:06.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 从早上就一直在烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.25,0:11:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你的烦恼又是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.49,0:11:14.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓 反正对我 你不会认真商谈的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.20,0:11:16.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没那回事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.64,0:11:19.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看脸就知道是否真的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.16,0:11:21.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.72,0:11:36.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没认真想
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是试试而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.12,0:11:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说说看 看情形我会帮你的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.87,0:11:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是可能因为太无聊而被你笑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使无聊 烦恼还是烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:49.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令 说清楚一定会清爽的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.46,0:11:50.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会听的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:51.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:52.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事情是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:58.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不出和樱老师独处的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:12:00.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的很无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.27,0:12:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个人 Impahal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.24,0:12:06.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆你也很辛苦的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.58,0:12:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有没有什么烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.71,0:12:08.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.24,0:12:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========PART2===========
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.53,0:12:29.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了阿忍 你有什么烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:31.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.49,0:12:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这位和尚想见樱老师
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.39,0:12:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才带他来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.30,0:12:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说你就是樱小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.77,0:12:39.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.57,0:12:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.96,0:12:44.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是健东寺的住持
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说有烦恼商榷室
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.29,0:12:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱持一丝希望而来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论如何请帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.01,0:12:55.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是本校未对与本校无关之人开放此项服务
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:58.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否网开一面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.74,0:13:01.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请对老人施与爱心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.28,0:13:02.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请抬头吧 老和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经对那些无聊的烦恼厌烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.51,0:13:07.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是像样的烦恼就接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.24,0:13:12.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是犹如菩萨般的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:19.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是来商榷烦恼的吗？秃驴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.42,0:13:22.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有关此乃是我没有敲钟的人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.25,0:13:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敲钟的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.72,0:13:26.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是先代住持的冥诞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.69,0:13:27.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此遗言
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.19,0:13:31.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得在今晚敲一千次的钟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.27,0:13:32.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一千次 这可真辛苦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.14,0:13:37.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是寺中之人全都弄坏身体无法敲钟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.90,0:13:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照这样下去无颜对先人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.86,0:13:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想以死谢罪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.76,0:13:45.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要说丧气话 和尚
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:48.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有能代替敲钟的就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是没那么容易找到可以敲千次钟的人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.07,0:13:52.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:55.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本校有许多具有蓬勃生气的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.00,0:13:56.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.82,0:13:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆 龙之介 阿忍 面堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.55,0:14:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可准备了厚礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:03.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礼？是钱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.59,0:14:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以买胸罩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也拜托你们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.75,0:14:11.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家合力一定有办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.12,0:14:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是樱老师说的 做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.70,0:14:16.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诸星你还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.83,0:14:18.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱持日日对樱老师的爱念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:20.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不断敲着心钟的我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:25.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚将我全部的爱响彻整个城市
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.43,0:14:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是在这石阶之上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.44,0:16:30.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早听说你们的寺庙修行艰苦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.89,0:16:32.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不同凡响
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:40.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是和尚你真有精神
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身体真的弄坏了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.06,0:16:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人真的不能老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.27,0:16:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马上到敲钟室
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:53.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个啊 人真的不能老啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:19.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.26,0:17:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这真壮观
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.69,0:17:26.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是奇特的钟室
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.93,0:17:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像拳击场
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.43,0:17:30.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且没有敲钟柱...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.88,0:17:47.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:52.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等等 你们误会什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么误会嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:56.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要看这状况 就一目了然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.33,0:17:59.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用自己的肉体作为钟锤
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.82,0:18:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将整个身体撞上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.41,0:18:12.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,答对了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.54,0:18:14.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 当然会弄坏身子了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.04,0:18:16.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是比听说还辛苦的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.49,0:18:20.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本也不想靠年轻人敲锤的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.10,0:18:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:24.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞天十字攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:29.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此没劲的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎能传到已逝先人耳中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我干
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:35.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要钱
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.14,0:18:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.50,0:18:42.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钱准备了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.11,0:18:44.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:48.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大葛笼 小葛笼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.41,0:18:53.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想由敲钟次数让人选自己要的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:54.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.35,0:18:58.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住持也是拼了命才准备了如此多的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.07,0:19:01.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在不做也不划算吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.36,0:19:03.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解了 我接受
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我要先说明
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.56,0:19:07.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是为钱而敲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.39,0:19:09.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家能了解
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:13.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类微小的好意绝不受制于物欲
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.16,0:19:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说不是因为钱而是为色吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.28,0:19:20.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去敲钟除去烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这声 这就是镇魂之声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:29.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.76,0:19:34.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:43.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,柔弱的拉姆小姐是做不来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆真可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:48.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.28,0:19:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安心吧 大葛笼我一定拿到
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.07,0:19:53.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令真温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.19,0:19:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为我拿最大的葛笼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.60,0:19:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是说我自己拿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.21,0:20:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.44,0:20:09.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来 阿忍尽情敲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.01,0:20:11.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 阿当
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.82,0:20:13.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.54,0:20:14.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,达令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.21,0:20:18.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么阻挠我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.79,0:20:20.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用达令太卑鄙了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.18,0:20:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我退下吧 你没什么腕力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.58,0:20:24.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.68,0:20:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才不会飞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.65,0:20:34.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双十字
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:45.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:52.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有 有那种的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.24,0:20:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真清爽的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.47,0:21:00.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不妙啊 这样大葛笼会被夺走的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.58,0:21:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有点危险 但已经没办法了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真清爽的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.94,0:21:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.83,0:21:19.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子还是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.62,0:21:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑 好窄 好可怕呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:33.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.91,0:21:37.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僧人 由内部敲算吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.85,0:21:40.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真清爽的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶 我不能输
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.85,0:21:46.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们也要加油
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.95,0:21:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行我也得赶上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.67,0:21:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱老师
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:21:58.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.82,0:22:04.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真清爽的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.25,0:22:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算在我的份上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.18,0:22:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真嘈杂的钟声
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.11,0:22:27.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安静点
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:29.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了没
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.71,0:22:37.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一千次
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.90,0:22:44.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这下先人的灵魂也为之告慰了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.68,0:22:46.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.71,0:22:49.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快给约定好的钱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.22,0:22:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.67,0:22:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请取葛笼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.19,0:23:07.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（日语中 钟【KANE】与钱同音）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.29,0:23:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,钟（钱）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.64,0:23:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要做这么多钟真是辛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.60,0:23:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但辛苦总算有代价了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.44,0:23:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面堂 你还有没有体力
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.49,0:23:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还多得很呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.92,0:23:25.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要干
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.20,0:23:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种玩笑我最讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.70,0:23:34.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樱小姐 今天真是辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.06,0:23:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由记忆的角落掉落的回忆项链
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.97,0:23:54.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旧伤痛起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:23:56.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在蒲公英草原失去的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:23:57.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在追赶
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:23:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这伤心接近中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:00.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.05,0:24:02.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再一次初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.61,0:24:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会回到以前吗？拉姆及阿雷
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.94,0:24:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,===========ED===========
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.41,0:24:27.69,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我独自的漫步在雨中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.69,0:24:30.74,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在从前...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.39,0:24:35.26,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到你出现时那一切是寒冷的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.26,0:24:38.33,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却还要故作姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.93,0:24:42.86,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宝贝 宝贝 你
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.87,0:24:46.83,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你改变了我的一切 哦！宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.83,0:24:49.04,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能否再受感动
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.04,0:24:55.28,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使每天更好...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.28,0:24:59.36,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天我沉浸在爱之中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.36,0:25:03.22,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你再爱我
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.22,0:25:07.06,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天你充满在我心中
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.06,0:25:10.85,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在梦中你使其真实
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.85,0:25:14.57,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天你带来阳光
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.57,0:25:18.64,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在整晚中追逐
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.64,0:25:22.31,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一天都是我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.31,0:25:26.87,ed,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期望你等着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.19,0:00:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,

